✨PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASING✨

HI THERE! 

*SCROLL ON DOWN. I HAVE LOTS OF DIFFERENT STUFF FOR SALE

* I DO NOT MODEL, TRADE OR HOLD.  NO EXCEPTIONS

* Please accept and rate your order once received.  I NEED THE MONEY. 

*PLEASE DO NOT MAKE OFFERS OR CREATE BUNDLES UNLESS YOU INTEND ON BUYING THE ITEMS*

Bundles or offers not purchased the same day will be deleted.

*IF YOU ARE RUDE OR PUSHY, I WILL BLOCK YOU. 

 * I’m more than happy to answer questions about any listing and will get back to you ASAP. Hit me up. I don’t bite 

* I almost always add the measurements of all the clothing I list. If the measurements aren’t listed, please ask and I’ll get them for you. 

* Please pay close attention to measurements and descriptions before purchasing anything. 

**ALL SALES ARE FINAL**

* I will consider reasonable offers ONLY. 
* Lowball offers will be declined. Any offer that is over 20% off will be automatically declined.  
* If the listing says price is firm, I am not accepting offers. 

* I offer bundle discounts.
* I do not accept offers on bundles. There is already an automatic bundle discount is in place. Thats what the bundle discount feature is there for. 

* I provide same day or next day shipping. Items purchased between Friday afternoon and Sunday will be shipped on Monday. 
If there are any issues, I will always let you know. 

* Please keep in mind that once the item is taken to the post office, it is out of my hands. I am not responsible for what happens once your order is in the mail. 

🐾 I have cats. I don’t let them use my stuff as their personal beds or anything. Everything I list is kept in sealed tubs. Just a heads up in case you are allergic.🐾

* Smoke free home. 
* I use free/clear detergent only. No fabric softeners/dryer sheets. 

Thanks and have a super duper day! 

⚡️Maria⚡️
